<div class="title">With Various Recreational Drugs</div>
<div class="substance">Mirtazapine & Various</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Notspam&Exact=1">Notspam</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Notspam. "With Various Recreational Drugs: An Experience with Mirtazapine & Various (exp84876)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jul 21, 2010. erowid.org/exp/84876</div>

